<h1> 결투장 </h1>

<div>
    <form action='/start_fight' method='POST' style='border: 1px solid black;'>
        <h1>결투장</h1>
        To. <input type="text" name="to">
        <br><br>
        너에게
        <select name="city_id" id="city_id">
            <option value="1">학점대결</option>
            <option value="2">다이어트대결</option>
            <option value="3">e-sports대결</option>
            <option value="4">스포츠대결</option>
            <option value="5">자유대결</option>
        </select>
        를 신청한다.
        승리조건은 다음과 같다. <br>
        <textarea type="text" name="context"> </textarea> <br>
        From. <input type="text" name="from">
        <input type='submit'>
    </form>
</div>


